title: Protection: Codes of Conduct
description: Kaitlyn Marshall – Successful, beautiful, intelligent, and the daughter of the President of the United States of America.Evan Stewards – Not your average man in a suit. Secret Service Agent, brave, and reliable.When Kaitlyn’s life is in danger, she learns just how vital her Secret Service detail is to the protection of her life and heart.Codes of conduct are meant to be broken, aren’t they?
author: Janae Keyes
